#summary This is the Example 2 using the Java API

= Search all human proteins which are linked to one of the Ontologies in the Ontology List using the  Java API =

The Java Code for this example is [http://jbiowh.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/src/main/java/org/jbiowh/tools/examples/FindALLHumProtinGO.java here]
Go to a CMD Windows console or a linux console to execute the java code:

<code language="bash">
java -cp <path-to the-jbiowh-jar-file> org.jbiowh.tools.examples.FindALLHumProtinGO
</code>

The obtained proteins number is the same that in the others methods.
